def darken_blend_8(base, active):
    m = len(base)
    n = len(base[0])
    out = []
    for row in range(m):
        row_vec = []
        for col in range(n):
            pixel = reduce_max([active[row][col], base[row][col]])
            row_vec.append(pixel)
        out.append(row_vec)
    return out
